#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.26"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.26:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Saraṇānivagga"
msgstr "3. About Sarakāni"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 26. Paṭhamaanāthapiṇḍikasutta → dussilya or anāthapiṇḍika 1 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn55.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Paṭhamaanāthapiṇḍikasutta"
msgstr "26. Anāthapiṇḍika (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn55.26:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati ābādhiko hoti dukkhito "
"bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the householder Anāthapiṇḍika was sick, suffering, gravely "
"ill."

msgctxt "sn55.26:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati aññataraṃ purisaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then he addressed a man:"

msgctxt "sn55.26:1.4"
msgid ""
"“ehi tvaṃ, ambho purisa, yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkama; upasaṅkamitvā "
"mama vacanena āyasmato sāriputtassa pāde sirasā vanda:"
msgstr ""
"“Please, mister, go to Venerable Sāriputta, and in my name bow with your "
"head to his feet. Say to him:"

msgctxt "sn55.26:1.5"
msgid "‘anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr "‘Sir, the householder Anāthapiṇḍika is sick, suffering, gravely ill."

msgctxt "sn55.26:1.6"
msgid "So āyasmato sāriputtassa pāde sirasā vandatī’ti."
msgstr "He bows with his head to your feet.’"

msgctxt "sn55.26:1.7"
msgid "Evañca vadehi:"
msgstr "And then say:"

msgctxt "sn55.26:1.8"
msgid ""
"‘sādhu kira, bhante, āyasmā sāriputto yena anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa "
"nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’”ti."
msgstr "‘Sir, please visit him at his home out of compassion.’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.381"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho so puriso anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa paṭissutvā "
"yenāyasmā sāriputto tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so puriso āyasmantaṃ "
"sāriputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” that man replied. He did as Anāthapiṇḍika asked."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:3.1"
msgid "“Anāthapiṇḍiko, bhante, gahapati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:3.2"
msgid "So āyasmato sāriputtassa pāde sirasā vandati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:3.3"
msgid "Evañca vadati:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:3.4"
msgid ""
"‘sādhu kira, bhante, āyasmā sāriputto yena anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa "
"nivesanaṃ tenupasaṅkamatu anukampaṃ upādāyā’”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:3.5"
msgid "Adhivāsesi kho āyasmā sāriputto tuṇhībhāvena."
msgstr "Sāriputta consented in silence."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:4.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya "
"āyasmatā ānandena pacchāsamaṇena yena anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa nivesanaṃ "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. Nisajja kho āyasmā "
"sāriputto anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Sāriputta robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and "
"robe, went with Venerable Ānanda as his second monk to Anāthapiṇḍika’s home. "
"He sat down on the seat spread out, and said to Anāthapiṇḍika:"

msgctxt "sn55.26:4.2"
msgid ""
"“kacci te, gahapati, khamanīyaṃ kacci yāpanīyaṃ? Kacci dukkhā vedanā "
"paṭikkamanti, no abhikkamanti; paṭikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no abhikkamo”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Householder, I hope you’re coping; I hope you’re getting better. And I hope "
"the pain is fading, not growing, that its fading is evident, not its "
"growing.”"

msgctxt "sn55.26:4.3"
msgid ""
"“Na me, bhante, khamanīyaṃ, na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā "
"abhikkamanti, no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamo”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, I’m not keeping well, I’m not alright. The pain is terrible and "
"growing, not fading; its growing is evident, not its fading.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, buddhe appasādena samannāgato assutavā "
"puthujjano kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ "
"upapajjati tathārūpo te buddhe appasādo natthi."
msgstr ""
"“Householder, you don’t have the distrust in the Buddha that causes an "
"uneducated ordinary person to be reborn—when their body breaks up, after "
"death—in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "sn55.26:5.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, buddhe aveccappasādo—"
msgstr "And you have experiential confidence in the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn55.26:5.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti."
msgstr ""
"‘That Blessed One is perfected, a fully awakened Buddha, accomplished in "
"knowledge and conduct, holy, knower of the world, supreme guide for those "
"who wish to train, teacher of gods and humans, awakened, blessed.’"

msgctxt "sn55.26:5.4"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te buddhe aveccappasādaṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""
"Seeing in yourself that experiential confidence in the teaching, that pain "
"may die down on the spot."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.382"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:6.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, dhamme appasādena samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpo te dhamme appasādo natthi."
msgstr ""
"You don’t have the distrust in the teaching that causes an uneducated "
"ordinary person to be reborn—when their body breaks up, after death—in a "
"place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "sn55.26:6.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, dhamme aveccappasādo—"
msgstr "And you have experiential confidence in the teaching:"

msgctxt "sn55.26:6.3"
msgid "svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo … pe … paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhīti."
msgstr ""
"‘The teaching is well explained by the Buddha—realizable in this very life, "
"immediately effective, inviting inspection, relevant, so that sensible "
"people can know it for themselves.’"

msgctxt "sn55.26:6.4"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te dhamme aveccappasādaṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""
"Seeing in yourself that experiential confidence in the teaching, that pain "
"may die down on the spot."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:7.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, saṅghe appasādena samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpo te saṅghe appasādo natthi."
msgstr ""
"You don’t have the distrust in the Saṅgha that causes an uneducated ordinary "
"person to be reborn—when their body breaks up, after death—in a place of "
"loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "sn55.26:7.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, saṅghe aveccappasādo—"
msgstr "And you have experiential confidence in the Saṅgha:"

msgctxt "sn55.26:7.3"
msgid ""
"suppaṭipanno bhagavato sāvakasaṅgho … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassāti."
msgstr ""
"‘The Saṅgha of the Buddha’s disciples is practicing the way that’s good, "
"straightforward, methodical, and proper. It consists of the four pairs, the "
"eight individuals. This Saṅgha of the Buddha’s disciples is worthy of "
"offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a teacher’"
"s offering, and worthy of veneration with joined palms. It is the supreme "
"field of merit for the world.’"

msgctxt "sn55.26:7.4"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te saṅghe aveccappasādaṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""
"Seeing in yourself that experiential confidence in the Saṅgha, that pain may "
"die down on the spot."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:8.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, dussīlyena samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpaṃ te dussīlyaṃ natthi."
msgstr ""
"You don’t have the unethical conduct that causes an uneducated ordinary "
"person to be reborn—when their body breaks up, after death—in a place of "
"loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "sn55.26:8.2"
msgid ""
"Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, ariyakantāni sīlāni … pe samādhisaṃvattanikāni."
msgstr ""
"Your ethical conduct is loved by the noble ones, unbroken, impeccable, "
"spotless, and unmarred, liberating, praised by sensible people, not "
"mistaken, and leading to immersion."

msgctxt "sn55.26:8.3"
msgid ""
"Tāni ca pana te ariyakantāni sīlāni attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""
"Seeing in yourself that ethical conduct loved by the noble ones, that pain "
"may die down on the spot."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:9.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpāya kho, gahapati, micchādiṭṭhiyā samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpā te micchādiṭṭhi natthi."
msgstr ""
"You don’t have the wrong view that causes an uneducated ordinary person to "
"be reborn—when their body breaks up, after death—in a place of loss, a bad "
"place, the underworld, hell."

msgctxt "sn55.26:9.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammādiṭṭhi."
msgstr "You have right view."

msgctxt "sn55.26:9.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammādiṭṭhiṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr "Seeing in yourself that right view, that pain may die down on the spot."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:10.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, micchāsaṅkappena samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpo te micchāsaṅkappo natthi."
msgstr "You don’t have the wrong thought …"

msgctxt "sn55.26:10.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammāsaṅkappo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:10.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammāsaṅkappaṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.383"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:11.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpāya kho, gahapati, micchāvācāya samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpā te micchāvācā natthi."
msgstr "wrong speech …"

msgctxt "sn55.26:11.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammāvācā."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:11.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammāvācaṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:12.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, micchākammantena samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpo te micchākammanto natthi."
msgstr "wrong action …"

msgctxt "sn55.26:12.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammākammanto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:12.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammākammantaṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:13.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, micchāājīvena samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpo te micchāājīvo natthi."
msgstr "wrong livelihood …"

msgctxt "sn55.26:13.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammāājīvo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:13.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammāājīvaṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:14.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, micchāvāyāmena samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpo te micchāvāyāmo natthi."
msgstr "wrong effort …"

msgctxt "sn55.26:14.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammāvāyāmo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:14.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammāvāyāmaṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:15.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpāya kho, gahapati, micchāsatiyā samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpā te micchāsati natthi."
msgstr "wrong mindfulness …"

msgctxt "sn55.26:15.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammāsati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:15.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammāsatiṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:16.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, micchāsamādhinā samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpo te micchāsamādhi natthi."
msgstr "wrong immersion …"

msgctxt "sn55.26:16.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:16.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammāsamādhiṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.384"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:17.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpena kho, gahapati, micchāñāṇena samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpaṃ te micchāñāṇaṃ natthi."
msgstr "wrong knowledge …"

msgctxt "sn55.26:17.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammāñāṇaṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.26:17.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammāñāṇaṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyya."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:18.1"
msgid ""
"Yathārūpāya kho, gahapati, micchāvimuttiyā samannāgato assutavā puthujjano "
"kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati, "
"tathārūpā te micchāvimutti natthi."
msgstr "wrong freedom …"

msgctxt "sn55.26:18.2"
msgid "Atthi ca kho te, gahapati, sammāvimutti."
msgstr "You have right freedom."

msgctxt "sn55.26:18.3"
msgid ""
"Tañca pana te sammāvimuttiṃ attani samanupassato ṭhānaso vedanā "
"paṭippassambheyyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Seeing in yourself that right freedom, that pain may die down on the spot.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:19.1"
msgid "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa ṭhānaso vedanā paṭippassambhiṃsu."
msgstr "And then Anāthapiṇḍika’s pain died down on the spot."

msgctxt "sn55.26:19.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati āyasmantañca sāriputtaṃ āyasmantañca ānandaṃ "
"sakeneva thālipākena parivisi."
msgstr "Then he served Sāriputta and Ānanda from his own dish."

msgctxt "sn55.26:19.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ bhuttāviṃ "
"onītapattapāṇiṃ aññataraṃ nīcāsanaṃ gahetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"When Sāriputta had eaten and washed his hand and bowl, Anāthapiṇḍika took a "
"low seat and sat to one side."

msgctxt "sn55.26:19.4"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ āyasmā sāriputto imāhi "
"gāthāhi anumodi:"
msgstr ""
"Venerable Sāriputta expressed his appreciation to him with these verses."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:20.1"
msgid "“Yassa saddhā tathāgate,"
msgstr "“Whoever has faith in the Realized One,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.26:20.2"
msgid "acalā suppatiṭṭhitā;"
msgstr "unwavering and well grounded;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.26:20.3"
msgid "Sīlañca yassa kalyāṇaṃ,"
msgstr "whose ethical conduct is good,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.26:20.4"
msgid "ariyakantaṃ pasaṃsitaṃ."
msgstr "praised and loved by the noble ones;"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:21.1"
msgid "Saṃghe pasādo yassatthi,"
msgstr "who has confidence in the Saṅgha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.26:21.2"
msgid "ujubhūtañca dassanaṃ;"
msgstr "and correct view:"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Adaliddoti → adaḷiddoti (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn55.26:21.3"
msgid "Adaliddoti taṃ āhu,"
msgstr "they’re said to be prosperous,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.26:21.4"
msgid "amoghaṃ tassa jīvitaṃ."
msgstr "their life is not in vain."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:22.1"
msgid "Tasmā saddhañca sīlañca,"
msgstr "So let the wise devote themselves"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.26:22.2"
msgid "pasādaṃ dhammadassanaṃ;"
msgstr "to faith, ethical behaviour,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.26:22.3"
msgid "Anuyuñjetha medhāvī,"
msgstr "confidence, and insight into the teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn55.26:22.4"
msgid "saraṃ buddhānasāsanan”ti."
msgstr "remembering the instructions of the Buddhas.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:23.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā sāriputto anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ imāhi gāthāhi anumoditvā "
"uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"After expressing his appreciation to Anāthapiṇḍika with these verses, "
"Sāriputta got up from his seat and left."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.385"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.26:24.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ "
"bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The "
"Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "sn55.26:24.2"
msgid "“handa kuto nu tvaṃ, ānanda, āgacchasi divādivassā”ti?"
msgstr "“So, Ānanda, where are you coming from in the middle of the day?”"

msgctxt "sn55.26:24.3"
msgid ""
"“Āyasmatā, bhante, sāriputtena anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati iminā ca iminā ca "
"ovādena ovadito”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, Venerable Sāriputta advised the householder Anāthapiṇḍika in this way "
"and that.”"

msgctxt "sn55.26:24.4"
msgid "“Paṇḍito, ānanda, sāriputto;"
msgstr "“Sāriputta is astute, Ānanda."

msgctxt "sn55.26:24.5"
msgid ""
"mahāpañño, ānanda, sāriputto, yatra hi nāma cattāri sotāpattiyaṅgāni "
"dasahākārehi vibhajissatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"He has great wisdom, since he can analyze the four factors of stream-entry "
"in ten aspects.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.26:24.6"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
